label: SampleID -Wide
description: A field for recording the unique identifier for a sample in a wide, or combined long and wide table.

label: Airport IATA code
description: Airport IATA code for sampling, used as a parent site ID for organizing sub-sites in the airport.

label: Sample shed - wide
description: A geographic area, physical space, or structure. A sample is taken from a sampleshed for a representative measurement of a substance(s) in a wide, or combined long and wide table.

label: Site
description: A field for recording the unique identifier for a site in a wide, or combined long and wide table.

label: Population served (PE)
description: A field for reporting the attribute of a site, which specifies the population of/population served by a given site in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Collection start date/time - wide
description: For integrated time averaged samples this is the date, time and timezone the sample was started being taken in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Collection type - wide
description: The type of sample collection in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Composite collection number.period - wide
description: Composite collection number.period in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Pooled
description: Binary indicator for whether a sample is pooled/made by combining multiple distinct samples.

label: Analysis date/time start
description: Date, time, and timezone of when the analysis was started.

label: Analysis date/time end
description: Date, time, and timezone of when the analysis was completed.

label: Fraction analyzed
description: The fraction of the wastewater used for analysis and measurement.

label: Sample type
description: The type of sample.

label: Method used
description: The value for either the PCR method used, or the sequencing strategy used to obstain a measure in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Protocol citation link
description: Reference link for a specific protocol.

label: Target Type
description: The genetic "target type" as defined using ODM classes  in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Target
description: The genetic target or measure of an analysis  in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Target Other Specify
description: Value for an unlisted genetic target for either a mutation, an allele, or a variant  in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Value - wide
description: Measure value  in a wide or combined long-and-wide table where most details are recorded in other columns.

label: Unit - wide
description: The unit of a measure in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Aggregation - wide
description: The aggregation of a measure in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Sequence / Sequence URL
description: The reference link for a sequencing measure in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Chemical Oxygen Demand (mg/l)  - wide
description: Chemical oxygen demand in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Biochemical Oxygen Demand (mg/l) - wide
description: Biochemical oxygen demand in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Water conductivity (µS/cm) - wide
description: Wastewater or water conductivity  in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: pH - wide
description: pH of a site in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Nitrogen concentration (mg/l) - wide
description: Notal nitrogen concentration at a site in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Limit of Detection (gc) - wide
description: Limit of Detection of a wastewater sample in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Limit of Quantification (gc) - wide
description: Limit of quantification in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Report date - wide
description: Date that the measurement was reported to authorities in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Contact person email - wide
description: Contact email address in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.

label: Notes - wide
description: Notes on a measure in a wide or combined long-and-wide table.
